            <scopecontent id="aspace_c69af7f48f7256f44a3fd610da335934">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This series consists of writings and other material about Celia Shapiro, and is divided into three sections: book manuscripts, memoirs of Boris Shapiro, and other material. The book manuscripts consist of typed and written drafts with photographs, letters, and clippings inserted into the text. The material originally contained in Binder #1 appears to be part of the written manuscript; however, it has been kept separately in its original page order. Photographs in Binder #2 have been removed to the photograph series.</p>
            </scopecontent>
